{
  "stem": "13690.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 16.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So one day, my brother disguised himself as a lady, because he was known as a boy.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he dressed himself up as a girl.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He had blond hair.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He had no big beard, so to say.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was young, too-- he was three years older.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he walked out in the market day barefoot, because there was no shoes that-- ladies' shoes could fit his legs.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he was walking barefoot in the market, going into that house and telling the people that he was sent by this and this family, by his uncle and aunt-- and not even-- he did not say 'uncle,' but sent by this man and to give money for the child, which they prepaid, and so on.",
      "word_count": 56
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So that's the time when really it started.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Go ahead.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was-- if I recall, Eli left the hiding place a few times, which normally, shouldn't have been done.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One time, I think he went out because of the sickness of my sister to the drugstore.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And one time, he went also to-- to change-- to get a gold coin, to sell some gold for currency.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this was the two times that I do recall that he went out.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, he did not as-- he was disguised.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We stayed in Mr.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Placzek house for 18 months.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The problem-- I started to tell you.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When we got this letter from the relatives to help, and Eli decided to go to help, we were a very close-knitted family.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Until this day, we are very close.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He went to this Gentile to pay for the child, because my uncle prepaid only for, let's say, for one year.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And now, it was more, so he prepaid.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
